al2Role:"SaaS Founder",testimonial3Text:"Selling internationally used to be a nightmare. With Bluen it became simple and fast.",testimonial3Role:"E-commerce",testimonial4Text:"Brain showed me I was losing money on the downsell. I fixed it and recovered 23% of revenue.",testimonial4Role:"Creator",testimonial5Text:"Beautiful, fast checkout with real urgency. My conversion went from 2.8% to 4.5%.",testimonial5Role:"Copywriter",testimonial6Text:"End-to-end tracking saved our operation. Now we know exactly where each sale comes from.",testimonial6Role:"Digital Agency",testimonial7Text:"I migrated from another platform and was selling more within a week. Incredible interface.",testimonial7Role:"Coach",testimonial8Text:"The visual funnel is genius. I see exactly where I'm losing conversion.",testimonial8Role:"Digital Producer",testimonial9Text:"The AI gave me insights I'd never have figured out on my own. Like having a 24/7 consultant.",testimonial9Role:"Educator",pricingTag:"Pricing",pricingTitle:"Only pay when you sell.",pricingSubtitle:"No monthly fees. No setup. One transparent, global rate.",pricingMethod:"Method",pricingDomestic:"Domestic",pricingInternational:"International",pricingRelease:"Release",pricingInstant:"Instant",pricingBadge1:"No monthly fee",pricingBadge2:"No setup fee",pricingBadge3:"Settle in D+5",pricingBadge4:"Support included",pricingBadge5:"D+2 advance",pricingHeroLabel:"One transparent, global rate",pricingHeroSuffix:"per approved transaction",pricingPerkRelease:"Settle in D+5",pricingPerkAdvance:"Settle in up to D+2",pricingStatMethods:"100+ payment methods",pricingStatCurrencies:"30+ currencies",pricingStatCountries:"190+ countries",pricingMethodsTitle:"Payment methods accepted",pricingGroupCards:"Cards",pricingGroupWallets:"Digital wallets",pricingGroupBNPL:"Buy now, pay later",pricingGroupLocal:"Local methods",pricingFootnote:"PIX and selected local methods may have regional rates — talk to our team.",pricingMethodsSubtitle:"These are the main ones. We accept 100+ methods in total.",pricingExtraTitle:"Additional fees",pricingExtraFee1Label:"Currency conversion",pricingExtraFee1Value:"+1%",pricingExtraFee1Note:"When selling in a currency different from yours",pricingExtraFee2Label:"Chargeback fee",pricingExtraFee2Value:"US$ 40",pricingExtraFee2Note:"Refunded if you win the dispute",pricingExtraFee3Label:"Bank payout",pricingExtraFee3Value:"US$ 3",pricingExtraFee3Note:"Per processed payout",faqTag:"FAQ",faqTitle:"Frequently asked questions",faqQ1:"Can I sell to other countries with Bluen?",faqA1:"Yes. Bluen supports sales in 190+ countries, with multi-currency checkout and local payment methods.",faqQ2:"Does Bluen work for ebooks, courses, SaaS and e-commerce?",faqA2:"Yes. The platform was designed to serve all these business models with adapted checkout, funnels and analytics.",faqQ3:"How do sales funnels work?",faqA3:"You create a visual flow with sales page, checkout, upsell, downsell and thank-you page. Each step is tracked for optimization.",faqQ4:"Does tracking cover the entire funnel?",faqA4:"Yes. From the ad to the last funnel page, including conversion tracking for Meta, Google and TikTok.",faqQ5:"What does Bluen Brain do in practice?",faqA5:"It analyzes your account data and generates actionable recommendations: identifies bottlenecks, highlights priorities and suggests actions to increase revenue.",faqQ6:"Can I sell subscriptions?",faqA6:"Yes. Bluen supports recurring billing with MRR view, churn, recovery and complete subscription management.",faqQ7:"Can I customize my checkout?",faqA7:"Yes. Colors, logo, copy, urgency, social proof and payment methods are fully customizable.",faqQ8:"Do I need to use multiple separate tools?",faqA8:"No. Bluen combines checkout, funnels, tracking, analytics and AI in a single integrated platform.",faqQ9:"Who appears as the seller on my customer's invoice?",faqA9:"Bluen is the seller on all transactions processed through the platform. Your customer sees 'BLOOPI*' on their card statement and receives the receipt in Bluen's name. This protects you from direct disputes and ensures a professional buying experience for your customers.",faqQ10:"What does it mean for Bluen to be a Merchant of Record (MOR)?",faqA10:"As Merchant of Record, Bluen takes legal and tax responsibility for every transaction. You create and deliver the product; we handle payment, taxes, compliance and buyer support in each jurisdiction. That's why customers see BLOOPI* on their card statement.",faqQ11:"Can I sell through affiliates?",faqA11:"Yes. The native affiliate program lets you recruit partners that distribute your product. You set the commission, and Bluen handles attribution, tracking, receipt, support and affiliate payouts.",affiliatesTag:"Distribution",affiliatesTitle:"Native affiliate program.",affiliatesSubtitle:"Distribute your product through affiliates or partners pre-approved by the platform. Commissioning, attribution and payout — automated. No external tool needed.",affiliatesFeature1:"Manual or automatic affiliate approval",affiliatesFeature2:"Customizable commissions per product",affiliatesFeature3:"Complete attribution tracking",affiliatesFeature4:"Automated payouts to affiliates",affiliatesHighlight:"More than payments.",affiliatesHighlightGradient:"Distribution at scale.",ctaTitle:"Your next customer could be in any country.",ctaSubtitle:"Start selling globally with checkout, funnels, tracking and AI in a single platform.",ctaButton:"Start free",ctaBadge1:"190+ countries",ctaBadge2:"Full funnel",ctaBadge3:"Exclusive AI",ctaBadge4:"Global checkout",footerDesc:"Bluen is the platform to sell globally, optimize revenue and grow with intelligence.",footerProduct:"Product",footerResources:"Resources",footerLegal:"Legal",footerCompliance:"Compliance",footerCheckout:"Checkout",footerFunnels:"Funnels",footerAnalytics:"Analytics",footerBrainAI:"Brain (AI)",footerDocs:"Documentation",footerIntegrations:"Integrations",footerPricing:"Pricing",fo